  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我們來畫一個工業語音翻譯系統的狀態圖吧。核心裝置是ActuatorController，它會經過Idle、Recording、Processing、Playing這幾個主要狀態，最後還要有Error處理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing",
        "Playing",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，那系統啟動時是從ActuatorController進入Idle狀態對嗎？還有，Recording結束後除了正常進入Processing，使用者能不能中途取消？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "沒錯，初始化後進入Idle。使用者確實可以取消錄音，所以Recording要有兩條出路：正常結束到Processing，或者取消回到Idle。另外Processing也要分流，TTS啟用時走Playing，停用時直接回Idle顯示文字。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing",
        "Playing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把這些轉換加上去了。那Error狀態呢？一般錯誤和嚴重錯誤的處理方式應該不同吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "對，Error要有兩種恢復路徑：使用者確認後回到Idle，但如果是嚴重錯誤，系統要終止並連接到MQTT Broker回報。對了，Processing失敗也會進入Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Playing結束後也是回到Idle對嗎？使用者能不能在播放中途打斷？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，播放完成或使用者中斷都回到Idle。最後幫我在Recording和Processing旁邊加上註解，說明VAD監控、ASR轉錄這些技術細節。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle",
        "Recording",
        "Processing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
